  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170410/extras/78d62f317a392032e477f38751125e47.avif?t=1713217100\" width=560 height=215 /></span><br>Phantom Tides is a 2D action adventure platformer where find yourself captain of a pirate ship seeking crew members and venturing through various environments on your path to vengeance.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Explore and carve your own path<br></li><li> Unlock abilities and Items<br></li><li> Befriend or cross characters throughout your journey<br></li><li> Encounter a wide variety of enemies<br></li><li> Challenging bosses and puzzles</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170410/extras/f1b988088e5f52c27fb41af4e4baee3d.avif?t=1713217100\" width=560 height=214 /></span>",
